## Restore Wallpaper
sh $HOME/.fehbg

## add permission to every file
chmod +x ~/.config/*

## xfce4-settings daemon
xfsettingsd &

## Start Compositing Manager
ob-compositor --start &
sleep 2

## Launch Polybar
sh ~/.config/polybar/launch.sh

## Start Music Player Daemon
mpd &

## Thunar Daemon
thunar --daemon &
